        THE_AMOUNT_OF_GUILD_POINTS_YOU_WILL_RECEIVE                               = 7132,  -- The amount of guild points you will receive varies with the item requested, and there is a limit to how many points you can accumulate during the designated time frame. Trading items after you have reached the limit will result in no points gained.
