        AH_WELCOME_YOUNG_MAN_LADY_TO_THE_GOLDSMITHS                               = 7166,  -- Ah, welcome, young man/lady], to the Goldsmiths' Guild. This is a special association for those who work with silver, gold, gems, and all precious materials.
        IF_YOU_HAVE_NO_INTEREST_IN_JOINING_OUR                                    = 7167,  -- If you have no interest in joining our selected few, then off with you. There are no guided tours here.
        WONDERFUL_YOU_ARE_ONE_OF_THOSE_WHAT_DO                                    = 7168,  -- Wonderful... You are one of those...what do they call them...adventurers, are you not? I think we shall start you off with crystal synthesis.
        I_M_SURE_YOU_ALREADY_KNOW_BUT_CRYSTALS                                    = 7169,  -- I'm sure you already know, but crystals are a form of condensed energy. Using crystal synthesis draws the energy from the crystals, and uses that energy to convert matter into different forms.
        IT_SOUNDS_SIMPLE_BUT_TRUE_WORKS_OF_ART                                    = 7170,  -- It sounds simple, but true works of art can only be made by forming an image of the item when you synthesize. The better the image, the better chances you have of getting a product worth keeping.
        THAT_S_WHY_PROFESSIONAL_GOLDSMITHS_SUCH_AS_MYSELF                         = 7171,  -- That's why professional goldsmiths such as myself can produce superior goods...but don't take it personally.
        OUR_GUILD_DOES_NOT_PREFER_CRYSTAL_SYNTHESIS_TO                            = 7172,  -- Our guild does not prefer crystal synthesis to traditional methods, but if you ask the others here, I'm sure they will give you some good advice. They are all top-class artisans.
        THE_LONG_HISTORY_OF_GOLDSMITHING_TELLS_THE_NEVER                          = 7173,  -- The long history of goldsmithing tells the never-ending tale of man's pursuit for beauty. That history will continue as long as gold glitters. So, take your time, and start slowly.
        DO_YOU_REMEMBER_YOUR_FIRST_ACCESSORY_DO_YOU                               = 7174,  -- Do you remember your first accessory? Do you remember the person who wore it? No matter how skilled a goldsmith you become, you must never forget how you felt at that moment.
        IT_LOOKS_AS_IF_YOU_ARE_READY_TO                                           = 7175,  -- It looks as if you are ready to take the next step in your goldsmithing career. Try your hand at %.
        SUCCEED_AND_I_SHALL_GRACE_YOU_WITH_ANOTHER                                = 7176,  -- Succeed, and I shall grace you with another gem of knowledge.
        AH_THIS_IS_A_FAIR_EXAMPLE_OF_CRAFTSMANSHIP                                = 7177,  -- Ah, this is a fair example of craftsmanship. [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice] is the title you may wear. And remember...take your time. There is no need to rush things.
        AH_THIS_IS_A_FINE_EXAMPLE_OF_CRAFTSMANSHIP                                = 7178,  -- Ah, this is a fine example of craftsmanship.
        AH_THIS_IS_AN_EXCELLENT_EXAMPLE_OF_CRAFTSMANSHIP                          = 7179,  -- Ah, this is an excellent example of craftsmanship.
        THIS_THIS_IS_A_FABULOUS_EXAMPLE_OF_CRAFTSMANSHIP                          = 7180,  -- This... This is a fabulous example of craftsmanship... No, a fabulous work of art! You have more than earned the title of adept. There is little more I can teach you.
        THIS_IS_SO_BEAUTIFUL_I_THINK_I_WILL                                       = 7181,  -- This is so beautiful! I think I will be asking you to make all of my jewelry from now on!
