        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_OUR_VERY_OWN                                             = 7221,  -- Well, if it isn't our very own [veteran/expert/authority/luminary/master]. Quite some time has passed since you achieved your current rank. Are you perhaps ready to strive for greater heights?
        STRIVE_FOR_GREATER_HEIGHTS_CERTAINLY_MAYBE_LATER                          = 7222,  -- Strive for greater heights? Certainly! Maybe later...
        EXCELLENT_THAT_S_JUST_THE_ANSWER_I_WAS                                    = 7223,  -- Excellent! That's just the answer I was hoping to hear from our rising star. First, you'll want to speak to Ellard and obtain yourself %.
        SOME_GUILD_POINTS_WILL_BE_REQUIRED_FOR_THE                                = 7224,  -- Some guild points will be required for the transaction, but that should prove no obstacle for your considerable talents and devotion.
        A_SHAME_THAT_YOU_WOULD_ALLOW_YOUR_POTENTIAL                               = 7225,  -- A shame that you would allow your potential to go to waste. But I will hold no grudges. Should you ever have a change of heart, simply say the word.
        FIRST_YOU_LL_WANT_TO_SPEAK_TO_ELLARD                                      = 7226,  -- First, you'll want to speak to Ellard and obtain a copy of %.
        AH_YOU_VE_RETURNED_AND_THAT_LOOK_OF                                       = 7227,  -- Ah, you've returned. And that look of confidence on your face tells me you've already grasped the contents of %.
        VERY_WELL_THEN_YOUR_TASK_IS_TO_CRAFT                                      = 7228,  -- Very well, then. Your task is to craft %. Now I'll only say this once, so I encourage you to take notes. The ingredients you will need are...
