        AS_PEOPLE_WALK_THESE_STREETS_MOST_OF_THEM                                 = 7548,  -- As people walk these streets, most of them marvel at the Hume technology that was used in building the waterwheels and drawbridges of this city.
        BUT_WE_GALKA_WERE_THE_ONES_WHO_BUILT                                      = 7549,  -- But we Galka were the ones who built the foundations of Bastok, making it possible for those Hume contraptions to exist. Alas, Humes forget so easily...
        IT_S_EITHER_POORLY_GUARDED_POOR_HOUSES_OR                                 = 7550,  -- It's either poorly-guarded poor houses, or well-guarded well-to-do houses... How am I supposed to work under these conditions?
