        JUST_SOUTH_OF_THAT_INTERSECTION_IS_THE_ENTRANCE                           = 7579,  -- Just south of that intersection is the entrance to the Metalworks. You'll find the administrative buildings and forges there.
        IF_YOU_GO_FURTHER_SOUTH_YOU_LL_COME                                       = 7580,  -- If you go further south, you'll come to the central square. From there, you can access the West Gate, the Mines, and various shops.
        THE_ENTRANCE_TO_THE_RESIDENTIAL_AREA_IS_TO                                = 7581,  -- The entrance to the residential area is to the east. You can use the Mog Houses there.
        IF_YOU_GO_DOWN_THESE_STEPS_TOWARD_THE                                     = 7582,  -- If you go down these steps toward the north, you'll be able to see the entrance to Port Bastok.
        THIS_IS_THE_ENTRANCE_TO_THE_METALWORKS_THE                                = 7583,  -- This is the entrance to the Metalworks, the heart of Bastok.
        IN_IT_YOU_LL_FIND_THE_BLACKSMITHS_GUILD                                   = 7584,  -- In it you'll find the Blacksmiths' Guild, the forges, the consulates, and the President's Office.
        THIS_IS_THE_ENTRANCE_TO_PORT_BASTOK_THE                                   = 7585,  -- This is the entrance to Port Bastok. The air travel agency, the tavern, and the North Gate can all be found in the port.
        ON_THE_OTHER_SIDE_OF_THIS_CANAL_ARE                                       = 7586,  -- On the other side of this canal are the Goldsmiths' Guild and Carmelide's jewelry store.
