        HAH_YAH_I_M_STILL_ALIVE_AND_KICKIN                                        = 7660,  -- Hah! Yah! I'm still alive and kickin'! Do you want to know how I can be so energetic at my age? I'll tell you if you bring me the secret ingredient of my formula!
