        WHAT_IS_YOUR_BUSINESS_WOULD_YOU_CAST_SIGNET                               = 7829,  -- What is your business? Would you cast Signet on me? I want to spend my conquest points. [I want to join the Expeditionary Force./Teleport me to the E.F. area.] I want to quit the E.F./change my E.F. I want to go on a supplies quest. I have some questions... Nothing, sorry to bother you.
