        AYE_SPEAKIN_O_PEG_LEGS_THERE_BE_THIS                                      = 9510,  -- Aye, speakin' o' peg legs, there be this mighty fishy landlubber swaggerin' 'round Windurs' posin' as a smilebringer. What's that got t' do with peg legs? Arrrg, never ye mind.
