        THE_SABLE_SPIRIT_OF_DIABOLOS_LOOMS_IN_YOUR                                = 9735,  -- The sable spirit of Diabolos looms in your wake.
        JUST_AS_THE_RULER_OF_DREAMS_EXTENDS_HIS                                   = 9736,  -- Just as the ruler of dreams extends his nebulous arms to emancipate the righteous, you too harbor within your heart the strength to remain calm in dire straits, and lead those lambs who have strayed into the abyss to the light of victory.
