        OH_AND_HE_ALSO_SAYS_THAT_EVEN_THOUGH                                      = 9738,  -- Oh, and he also says that even though you may have the makings of a great man/woman], people will never follow you unless you tack some bravery and drive onto your resume. Go figure!
        THE_SCINTILLANT_SPIRIT_OF_CARBUNCLE_HOVERS_ABOVE_YOU                      = 9739,  -- The scintillant spirit of Carbuncle hovers above you.
        AND_JUST_AS_THE_DELICATE_RUBY_LIGHT_FROM                                  = 9740,  -- And just as the delicate ruby light from the bringer of rainbows soothes the weary soul, so too does the soft, warm radiance that shines forth from your heart unto those in need.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_HE_S_SAYING_YOU_RE_2                                       = 9741,  -- In other words, he's saying you're always nice to people. You know, helping them out with their problems and stuff. If you're not already a white mage, maybe you should think of a profession change.
        OH_AND_HE_ALSO_SAYS_THAT_THE_ONLY                                         = 9742,  -- Oh, and he also says that the only way that people will ever respect you is if you help them without expecting something in return. Kind of like helping a kid get a New Year's gift without wanting some kind of reward when you're done, wouldn't you say?
        THE_DYNAMIC_SPIRIT_OF_RAMUH_WALKS_BY_YOUR                                 = 9743,  -- The dynamic spirit of Ramuh walks by your side.
        JUST_AS_THE_WORLD_GLOWS_WITH_HIS_ELECTRIC                                 = 9744,  -- Just as the world glows with his electric wisdom, your mind too glows with an infinite intelligence that sends shudders of excitement and awe throughout the masses.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_YOU_RE_A_SMART_GUY                                         = 9745,  -- In other words, you're a smart guy/lady] who is chock full of curiosity and is always looking for a change. You wouldn't happen to be a red mage, would you?
        OH_AND_HE_ALSO_SAYS_THAT_IF_YOU                                           = 9746,  -- Oh, and he also says that if you would just pay a little more attention to those around you, people might not say all that bad stuff behind your back. Go figure!
        THE_LOFTY_SPIRIT_OF_TITAN_TOWERS_ABOVE_YOU                                = 9747,  -- The lofty spirit of Titan towers above you.
        JUST_AS_HIS_ADAMANTINE_WILL_SHIELDS_THE_MEAGER                            = 9748,  -- Just as his adamantine will shields the meager from destitution, you too tread the path of life with caution while providing sanctuary for all souls who gather in the warmth of your heart.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_YOU_THINK_BEFORE_YOU_ACT                                   = 9749,  -- In other words, you think before you act, unlike those creeps who shoot first and ask questions the next Firesday. Your ability to quickly identify an enemy's weak point and finish him off before he hurts your friends makes you good black mage material.
