        THE_WHISPERING_SPIRIT_OF_GARUDA_WHISKS_ABOUT_YOU                          = 9751,  -- The whispering spirit of Garuda whisks about you.
        JUST_AS_THE_AVATAR_OF_WIND_ROAMS_FREE                                     = 9752,  -- Just as the avatar of wind roams free across the never-ending skies of Vana'diel, so too does your lucid heart yearn to break free of the chains that bind it to conformity.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_HE_S_SAYING_THAT_YOU                                       = 9753,  -- In other words, he's saying that you were born to be an adventurer, and that your free spirit would make you a mighty good thief, if there is such thing as a good thief.
        OH_AND_HE_ALSO_SAYS_THAT_YOU_D                                            = 9754,  -- Oh, and he also says that you'd be a lot more popular if you'd stop trying to impress everyone and just be yourself. Go figure!
        THE_LUSTROUS_SPIRIT_OF_LEVIATHAN_WATCHES_OVER_YOU                         = 9755,  -- The lustrous spirit of Leviathan watches over you.
        JUST_AS_THE_RADIANT_VISAGE_OF_THE_GUARDIAN                                = 9756,  -- Just as the radiant visage of the guardian of seas renders vapid souls breathless, the pristine balance between your attention to beauty and respect for harmony are the waves upon which your companions cast their vessels.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_THAT_PRISTINE_BALANCE_HELPS_YOU                            = 9757,  -- In other words, that pristine balance helps you from being swayed by the poison opinions of others, and grants you good judgment in sticky situations. Add to that all that talk about harmony, and it sounds to me like you'd make a good bard.
        OH_AND_HE_ALSO_SAYS_THAT_IF_YOU_3                                         = 9758,  -- Oh, and he also says that if you'd stop worrying about what you wear on the outside and concentrated more on polishing what's inside, people might actually stop avoiding you. Go figure!
        THE_CHILLING_SPIRIT_OF_SHIVA_SHADOWS_YOUR_SOUL                            = 9759,  -- The chilling spirit of Shiva shadows your soul.
        AND_JUST_AS_HER_VEIL_OF_HOARFROST_HIDES                                   = 9760,  -- And just as her veil of hoarfrost hides the world from the eyes of men, you too don a shroud of discretion as you journey alone through the valleys of solitude.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_HE_S_SAYING_THAT_YOU_2                                     = 9761,  -- In other words, he's saying that you're a calm, cool, and collected player who has an answer for all the challenges life throws at you. Sounds like blue mage material to me!
        OH_AND_HE_ALSO_SAID_THAT_IF_YOU                                           = 9762,  -- Oh, and he also said that if you'd stop picking out people's faults and concentrate on what they've got on the inside, maybe you'll learn what true friendship is. Ouch!
