        JUST_AS_THE_MIGHTY_CONQUEROR_S_AMBITION_DRIVES                            = 9768,  -- Just as the mighty conqueror's ambition drives him to Victory's bosom, so too does the harmony within your heart guide stray souls to the paths they seek.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_HE_S_SAYING_THAT_YOUR                                      = 9769,  -- In other words, he's saying that your belief in your faith, along with your hating of all that is wrong, keeps your heart pure--pure enough to endure the trials of a paladin.
