        JUST_AS_THE_GUARDIAN_OF_THE_MOON_S                                        = 9772,  -- Just as the guardian of the moon's light drives darkness from the kingdom of night, you follow the sun across land and sky, from dawn until dusk, from birth until death. You see the world on a scale that dwarfs even the mightiest of mountains and their snow-laden peaks.
