        A_SUPER_SPECIAL_STARLIGHT_CELEBRATION_TO_YOU_AMBITIOUS                    = 14056,  -- A super-special Starlight Celebration to you, ambitious adventurer!
        WHAT_AM_I_SAYING_THIS_IS_HARDLY_THE                                       = 14057,  -- What am I saying!? This is hardly the time for gleeful greetings or alliterative addresses, kupo!
        EVEN_AS_WE_SPEAK_OVERZEALOUS_GOBLINS_ARE_PARTAKING                        = 14058,  -- Even as we speak, overzealous Goblins are partaking not just in the Starlight Celebration spirit, but others' precious presents! These Gobbies bear no bad blood, but their covetous capers are the cause of much consternation, kupo.
        AND_TO_MAKE_MATTERS_WORSE_THEY_VE_EVEN                                    = 14059,  -- And to make matters worse, they've even filched the furnishings the MHMU ordered from the guilds... I know the saying, If you give a Goblin goulash... but this is just rikupulous!
        PLEASE_I_BESEECH_YOU_FIND_THE_GOBLINS_TRAIPSING                           = 14060,  -- Please, %, I beseech you! Find the Goblins traipsing about town and teach them the meaning of private property once and for all! (By affably asking them to relinquish what they requisitioned, kupo.)
        IT_MAY_SEEM_LIKE_THE_MHMU_IS_JUST                                         = 14061,  -- It may seem like the MHMU is just exploiting the nearest adventurer, but nay! You--and only you--are capable of restoring resplendence and revelry to the realm. Now go forth and fulfill the festive fate we thrust upon you, kupo!
        KUPOPOPO_HAVE_YOU_FORGOTTEN_YOUR_MERRY_MISSION_ALREADY                    = 14062,  -- Kupopopo! Have you forgotten your merry mission already? Get giddy, gift-grabbing Goblins around town to give back people's goods, then go gab to a Moogle when you're done.
        AND_REMEMBER_GOBBIES_LIKE_TO_STICK_THEIR_NOSES                            = 14063,  -- And remember, Gobbies like to stick their noses in other creatures' business, if you know what I mean. Snuff out your smell so they can't sense your spoils, kupo.
        AND_REMEMBER_GOBLINS_GO_CUCKOO_FOR_COMESTIBLES_KUPO                       = 14064,  -- And remember, Goblins go cuckoo for comestibles, kupo. Offer them their favorite food, for they should forget you even exist.
        AND_REMEMBER_GOBLINS_JUST_WANT_TO_JUMP_FOR                                = 14065,  -- And remember, Goblins just want to jump for joy and jubilation at this jocular time of year. Bequeath beastmen bills or bedazzling bijoux to them and you may find yourself furnished with furnishings in return, kupo.
        GREAT_GLORIOUS_GODDESS_YOU_VE_MANAGED_TO_PROCURE                          = 14066,  -- Great glorious Goddess, you've managed to procure a present! Praise be to your positively prodigious persistence! ...And your altruistic attitude after you return it to its rightful remitter, kupo!
        IT_LOOKS_LIKE_THIS_GIFT_IS_FROM_SOMEONE                                   = 14067,  -- It looks like this gift is from someone named %. Seek out the sender and start spreading some Starlight spirit, kupo! Oh, and watch out for mischievous Goblin mitts, my little gofer--I mean adventurer!
        WONDERFUL_WORK_WARDEN_OF_WEAL_HOWEVER_SINCE_GIVING                        = 14068,  -- Wonderful work, warden of weal! However, since giving is greater than receiving, how about giving % word that you were able to deliver the present?
        THE_CONSIDERABLE_AMOUNT_OF_CHARITY_YOU_VE_SHOWN                           = 14069,  -- The considerable amount of charity you've shown complete strangers cannot be overstated, kupo. Without your magnanimity, moxie, and master mediation skills, this year's Starlight Celebration would have been a much dimmer affair.
        YET_TO_POLISH_THIS_PARTY_TO_THE_POINT                                     = 14070,  -- Yet to polish this party to the point of pristine luster, more Goblins must be taught the difference between naughty and nice! Remember, once you give back a gift, seal the deal by simply sauntering over to the nearest moogle. We're counting on you, kupo!
        THE_MHMU_HUMBLY_OFFERS_YOU_THIS_TOKEN_OF                                  = 14071,  -- The MHMU humbly offers you this token of our thanks, not only for making the world a brighter place, but for tolerating our moogle mummery and the voluminous vats of verbosity that violated your virgin ears.
        OH_DEAR_OH_DEAR_OH_DEAR_I_FORGOT                                          = 14072,  -- Oh dear, oh dear, oh dear! I forgot those festive Gobbies are still frolicking with our furnishings, kupo!
        I_M_SO_SORRY_TO_SOLICIT_FURTHER_FAVORS                                    = 14073,  -- I'm so sorry to solicit further favors from you, but could you kindly retrieve those as well? Pretty please with paprika on top? You wouldn't want to keep us from rewarding the good boys and girls of Vana'diel, would you, kupo?
        KUPO_HO_HO_DO_MY_DETERIORATING_EYES_DECEIVE                               = 14074,  -- Kupo ho ho! Do my deteriorating eyes deceive me, or is that one of the furnishings we ordered? We'd planned on giving them all to needy orphans, but you've done so much for the MHMU recently, why don't you have this one? 'Tis the season, so they say.
        WHAT_AN_ASTOUNDING_ACCOMPLISHMENT_AS_EXPECTED_OF_AN                       = 14075,  -- What an astounding accomplishment, as expected of an adventurer like you! We are eternally grateful for the copious kindnesses you've conferred upon us, kupo.
        WORD_AROUND_THE_UNION_FOUNTAIN_IS_THAT_OTHER                              = 14076,  -- Word around the union fountain is that other nations' furnishings still remain at large. Would it be too terrible a torment to traipse around town--peepers peeled for gregarious Gobbies ogling purported presents--the next time you visit another nation? The MHMU would be forever in your debt, kupo.
        WHEEEW_WAY_TO_WHISK_THAT_ONE_UNDER_THE                                    = 14077,  -- (Wheeew, way to whisk that one under the rug. I could never tell him/her] that we got distracted by the dazzling decorations and had the furnishings nabbed from nigh under our noses!)
        HAPPY_TOY_HAPPY_TOY_WHERE_BE_ME_HAPPY                                     = 14078,  -- Happy toy, happy toy, where be me happy toy?t
        EV_RY_GIRL_EV_RY_BOY_EV_RYBODY                                            = 14079,  -- Ev'ry girl, ev'ry boy, ev'rybody, happy toy! Me nose holes smell the joy, The joy from happy toy! Wheeere cooould iiit beee?t
        THIS_FOR_ME_IN_DOO_BID_ABLY_COULD                                         = 14080,  -- This for me? In-doo-bid-ably! Could be gooder, but it not bad.
        WAAAH_IT_YOU_YOU_GIVE_YUM_YUMS_FOR                                        = 14081,  -- Waaah! It you! You give yum-yums for me tum-tum. Good guy/girl]!
        NOT_FOR_US_NOT_FOR_ME_I_GIVE                                              = 14082,  -- Not for us, not for me? I give it back. Now you happy? Happy toy, happy toy, where be me happy toy?t
        NO_NO_NO_NO_NO_GO_AWAY_NOSE                                               = 14083,  -- No no no no no! Go away! Nose holes busy sniff for happy toy!
        ID_14084                                                                  = 14084,  -- ...
        YOU_HAVE_FRIEND_YOU_DO_WE_GOBBIES_HAVE                                    = 14085,  -- You have friend, you do? We Gobbies have friend too.
        YUM_YUMS_FOR_ME_GOBBIES_REMEMBER_TILL_OUR                                 = 14086,  -- Yum-yums for me? Gobbies remember...till our tummies go rumble-rumble again.
        FOR_ME_WHY_GIVE_SO_NICE_THING_TO                                          = 14087,  -- For me!? Why give so nice thing to me!? Me so happy head go boom! So boom! But first, me need give happy toy to you too.
        HAPPY_TOY_FOR_ME_WHY_YOU_GIVE_SO                                          = 14088,  -- Happy toy? For me? Why you give so good thing to me? But no can take. Me have no happy toy for you.
        BLECH_WHAT_THIS_YUCKY_THING_IT_MAKE_ME                                    = 14089,  -- Blech. What this yucky thing? It make me want upgut food. Take it away.
        WHAT_BUT_HOW_IF_THAT_S_TRULY_FROM                                         = 14090,  -- What? But how...? If that's truly from %, that must mean...you stole it and you're ransoming it back to me! If you think for one moment that I'd pay scum like you, you'd best think twice!
        OH_I_SEE_MY_APOLOGIES_HOW_SILLY_OF                                        = 14091,  -- Oh, I see. My apologies. How silly of me. Everyone knows how mischievous Goblins get during the Starlight Celebration season. I read somewhere that it's got something to do with the moon and the tides or whatnot.
        ANYWAY_SORRY_TO_TROUBLE_YOU_BUT_COULD_YOU                                 = 14092,  -- Anyway, sorry to trouble you, but could you deliver this in my stead? I may look like a strapping young lad, but I have this illness that prevents me from doing the same task twice in one day. Quite troublesome, really.
        ALSO_COULD_YOU_DO_ME_A_FAVOR_AND                                          = 14093,  -- Also, could you do me a favor and report back to me after you're done? I didn't want to spend the extra gil for delivery confirmation with times as tough as they are, you know?
        I_TAKE_IT_YOU_DELIVERED_MY_PRESENT_SAFE                                   = 14094,  -- I take it you delivered my present safe and sound? Oh, and it was well received, too? Ha, you didn't need to tell me that, for my gifts are always a hit. I guess I should thank you though, seeing as how you played a tiny part in my Starlight Celebration success.
        WAAAH_A_CUTTHROAT_TAKE_ANYTHING_YOU_WANT_JUST                             = 14095,  -- Waaah, a cutthroat! Take anything you want, just not my lucky chocobo hose, please! I... Wait, isn't that the gift I sent %? You didn't steal that too, did you!?
        WHAT_YOU_VALIANTLY_WRESTED_IT_FROM_THE_CLUTCHES                           = 14096,  -- What!? You...valiantly wrested it from the clutches of a greedy Goblin so you could return it to me? I just knew my handsome champion/fair handmaiden] in resplendent regalia would come some day!
        I_M_SURE_YOU_VE_BEEN_THROUGH_QUITE                                        = 14097,  -- I'm sure you've been through quite a few trials and tribulations just getting this back to me, your fair lady. However, my hands are tied at the moment and I can't take this present to %. Therefore, I command you, my loyal follower, to act as my liaison and deliver it unscathed. I have no doubt that you'll succeed, since a knight/handmaiden] will do anything to serve and protect his/her] mistress.
        AND_PLEASE_DON_T_FORGET_TO_CHECK_IN                                       = 14098,  -- And please don't forget to check in with me after the delivery is made. Every champion/handmaiden] knows that's the chivalrous/proper] thing to do.
        HOW_FARED_YOUR_JOURNEY_MY_COURAGEOUS_CHAMPION_HUMBLE                      = 14099,  -- How fared your journey, my courageous champion/humble handmaiden]? Oh, I simply knew I could place my complete trust in you! You've not only made your fair lady quite proud, but saved the Starlight Celebration from those covetous beastmen! Oh, joyous day!
        I_BEG_YOUR_PARDON_BUT_I_CANNOT_HELP                                       = 14100,  -- I beg your pardon, but I cannot help but notice that this is the parcel I sent to %. How might you have come by it?
        AH_I_SEE_THOSE_GOBLIN_RAPSCALLIONS_STILL_SHOW                             = 14101,  -- Ah, I see. Those Goblin rapscallions still show a complete and utter disregard for social graces, would you not agree? At any rate, you seem to possess a rather strong sense of justice, and for that I am most grateful.
        COULD_YOU_ALSO_FIND_IT_WITHIN_YOUR_HEART                                  = 14102,  -- Could you also find it within your heart to see that this package reaches % safely? I may be a man of humble means, but you will certainly have my eternal gratitude and undying admiration.
        OH_MY_THIS_UTTERLY_SLIPPED_MY_ADDLED_MIND                                 = 14103,  -- Oh my. This utterly slipped my addled mind. I am truly sorry, but I fear I must heap one more request upon your already burdened back. Could you please report back to me after you've made the delivery? It would undoubtedly lessen the anxiety weighing down my fragile heart.
        GODDESS_BE_GOOD_YOU_HAVE_RETURNED_AND_WITH                                = 14104,  -- Goddess be good, you have returned! And with favorable tidings, no? Splendid. Absolutely splendid. Thanks to you, I feel as if I could burst into a Starlight carol at any moment. Fa-la-la-la`t.
        WHAT_DOTH_BRING_THEE_FORE_THESE_RHEUMY_EYES                               = 14105,  -- What doth bring thee 'fore these rheumy eyes, orbs that pierce the soul and a stranger's guise? Harken, thou hast %'s present, from whom hast thou received such consent?
        TIS_AN_ENTERTAINING_TALE_WITH_WHICH_THY_JOWLS                             = 14106,  -- 'Tis an entertaining tale with which thy jowls doth flail, A tale of Goblins run amok, and wretched me bereft of luck. Still, thanks are in store for completing this chore with a dearth of gore.
        WHILE_THESE_NEXT_WORDS_MAY_CONJURE_A_STORM                                = 14107,  -- While these next words may conjure a storm, I cannot assist thee in any form. Thus, I entreat thee to heed the call...deliver this gift to % once and for all!
        FORE_I_FINISH_THIS_LENGTHY_TIRADE_ONE_LAST                                = 14108,  -- 'Fore I finish this lengthy tirade, one last request must be made. Once the gift hath changed hands, return at once for further plans.
        THOU_HAST_SAFELY_RETURNED_FROM_THY_TRIAL_UPON                             = 14109,  -- Thou hast safely returned from thy trial? Upon us both doth Altana smile! To thee, the savior of the Starlight Celebration, I do give heartfelt acclamations!
        WH_WH_WHAT_HAVE_YOU_GOT_THERE_IT                                          = 14110,  -- Wh-wh-what have you got there? It looks awfully-wafully like the gift I gave to %. Did something happen? P-p-please don't tell me that % passy-wassed away!
        IT_WAS_JUST_A_G_G_GOBLIN_PRANK                                            = 14111,  -- ...It was just a G-g-goblin prank? Sorry to overreactaru. I had a t-t-traumatic experience last Starlight Devastation--er, Celebration! So now I always feary-wear the worst. By the way, th-th-thank you for getting my gift back.
        AS_YOU_CAN_GUESS_M_M_MY_COMFORT                                           = 14112,  -- As you can guess, m-m-my comfort zone is rather itty-bitty. I know you must be expired--tired! But can you please helpy-welp me and deliver my present to %?
        AFTER_YOU_PASS_ON_THE_GIFT_PASS_THE                                       = 14113,  -- After you pass on--the gift! Pass the gift on! Then c-c-could you report back to me? I truly-wuly want to know how % reacts.
        AH_YOU_RE_BACK_IT_S_S_MOST                                                = 14114,  -- Ah, you're back! It's %'s most perished, er, cherished possession, you say? Wh-wh-what lofty-wofty praise! I can't thank you enough for your c-c-contributions, adventurer.
        SO_MANY_NASTY_WASTY_THINGS_HAPPENED_TO_ME                                 = 14115,  -- So many nasty-wasty things happened to me today, I'm just too moody-woody to listen to your blather! Begone before I--wait, isn't that my present to %?
        UGH_QUIT_BARKING_LIKE_A_BOG_DOG_BROTHER                                   = 14116,  -- Ugh, quit barking like a bog dog, brother-wother/sister-wister]! I don't give a ham and cheese about giddy Goblins or lazy moogles.
        YOU_THINK_YOU_RE_SO_GREAT_BECAUSE_YOU                                     = 14117,  -- You think you're so great because you saved my present from some baddie-waddies? Bah humbug-wumbug! If you're gonna stick your nosey-wose in others' business, then you bettaru finish what you started! You'll be taking that gift on over to %, I tell you what!
        AND_DON_T_THINK_FOR_A_MINUTE_WINUTE                                       = 14118,  -- And don't think for a minute-winute that I'm going to let you get away with ruining my day! Report back here for a tongue-lashing when you're done! Now get going before I gutaru you right here and now!
        HMPH_SO_YOU_RE_STUPID_AS_WELL_AS                                          = 14119,  -- Hmph, so you're stupid as well as rude? Are you so subservient that you'd actually come backy-wack for a beating? Get out of my face! You disgustaru me. Oh, and Merry Starlight!
        HEY_I_SENT_THAT_TO_WHY_DO_YOU                                             = 14120,  -- Hey, I sent that to %. Why do you have it?
        HMMM_STOLEN_BY_GOBBIES_HUH_THANKS_FOR_GETTING                             = 14121,  -- Hmmm. Stolen by Gobbies, huh? Thanks for getting it back.
        SORRY_TO_BURDEN_YOU_BUT_COULD_YOU_BRING                                   = 14122,  -- Sorry to burden you, but could you bring it to % again for me?
        ALSO_I_D_LIKE_IT_IF_YOU_COULD                                             = 14123,  -- Also, I'd like it if you could please fill me in when you're done.
        I_SEE_YOU_VE_RETURNED_MMM_THAT_S                                          = 14124,  -- I see you've returned. Mmm...that's good news indeed. Thank you for the kindness you've shown me and my friend.
        WHAT_HAVE_WE_HERE_A_CAT_BURRRGLAR_HOW                                     = 14125,  -- What have we here? A cat burrrglar? How dare you despoil the innocent people of our fair nation!
        WHAT_AM_I_TALKING_ABOUT_THAT_S_THE                                        = 14126,  -- What am I talking about? That's the prrresent I sent %! How could you have it if you didn't steal it!?
        OH_I_SEE_YOU_RE_A_DEFENDER_OF                                             = 14127,  -- Oh, I see. You're a defender of justice too. Good job negotiating with those Goblin scum. I just hope that rrrepeating that story to everyone you've saved hasn't got you hacking up hairballs.
        BUT_ENOUGH_TAIL_WAGGING_I_HAVE_SOME_PREY                                  = 14128,  -- But enough tail wagging. I have some prey I need to take care of, so could you rrredeliver that gift to % and report back to me when you're done?
        WHAT_TIMING_I_VE_JUST_RRRETURNED_FROM_MY                                  = 14129,  -- What timing! I've just rrreturned from my own mission. Whew, good thing % liked it! That little trinket was as high priced as the hair on a cat's back! Anyway, thanks for your help. If your fur ever gets rubbed the wrong way, give me a sign and I'll come rrroaring to the rescue!
        A_PRESENT_FROM_OH_GLORIOUS_DAY_THIS_IS                                    = 14130,  -- A present...from %? Oh, glorious day! This is for all those times I never got a present and kept telling myself next year will be the one.
        I_M_AT_A_LOSS_FOR_WHAT_TO                                                 = 14131,  -- I'm at a loss for what to say! I'm just overwhelmed with a waterfall of emotion! Thank you so much!
        AND_PLEASE_THANK_THE_NEXT_TIME_YOU_SEE                                    = 14132,  -- And please thank % the next time you see that good samaritan. The person who said, 'Tis better to give than receive probably never had a gift drought as long as mine. I feel fantastic!
        OH_IS_THAT_A_PRESENT_FROM_YOU_SAY                                         = 14133,  -- Oh, is that...a present? From %, you say?
        UGH_IT_FIGURES_DID_IT_COME_WITH_A                                         = 14134,  -- Ugh, it figures. Did it come with a card that says something pathetic like I've died a thousand deaths drowning in the depths of your eyes? That scoundrel has been stalking me ever since we happened to meet one day on a boat to Buburimu Peninsula.
        I_M_ACTUALLY_QUITE_FED_UP_WITH_THESE                                      = 14135,  -- I'm actually quite fed up with these ridiculous baubles, but I'm not one for losing face. If you should see % again, please give my regards and say I found the gift rather...quaint.
        WHAT_S_THIS_A_PRESENT_ADDRESSED_TO_ME                                     = 14136,  -- What's this? A present addressed to me from %?
        HOW_UNEXPECTEDLY_CHARMING_AND_THOUGHTFUL_THIS_HAS_CERTAINLY               = 14137,  -- How unexpectedly charming and thoughtful. This has certainly brightened what was about to be a gloomy Starlight Celebration.
        WOULD_YOU_BE_SO_KIND_AS_TO_TELL                                           = 14138,  -- Would you be so kind as to tell % that I truly appreciate the gift? I am also thoroughly impressed with your selfless nature, adventurer.
        COULD_IT_BE_INDEED_IT_IS_BENEVOLENCE_MANIFEST                             = 14139,  -- Could it be...? Indeed, it is benevolence manifest, emanating from the humble home of one %?
        WHAT_A_DECIDEDLY_PLEASANT_SURPRISE_I_AM_SIMPLY                            = 14140,  -- What a decidedly pleasant surprise. I am simply beside myself with an unbridled, childish glee that has not washed over me in ever so long. I swear that I am on the brink of giggling like I used to when I was still knee-high to a Taru.
        THE_FINITE_WORDS_OF_US_MERE_MORTALS_MAY                                   = 14141,  -- The finite words of us mere mortals may not be sufficient to convey the depths of my gratitude, but I earnestly hope % would appreciate a succinct Thank you.
        A_PRESENT_FROM_THIS_ISN_T_ONE_OF                                          = 14142,  -- A present from...%? This isn't one of those tricky-wicky flimflams, is it?
        OF_COURSE_I_LL_TAKE_IT_I_M                                                = 14143,  -- Of course I'll take it! I'm not one to look a gift horse in the mouth, even if it's from my mortaru enemy! Maybe % has turned over a new leaf since we last met...
        WELL_THEN_I_SUPPOSE_SOME_THANKS_ARE_IN                                    = 14144,  -- Well then, I suppose some thanks are in order. But if I find out that this was just some elaborataru scheme to make me lower my guard, I'm going to boppy-wop you both in the noggin!
        OOOH_A_GIFT_FROM_WHAT_JOLLY_WOLLY_TIDINGS                                 = 14145,  -- Oooh, a gift from %? What jolly-wolly tidings you've brought, adventurer.
        I_WONDER_WHAT_S_INSIDE_COULD_IT_BE                                        = 14146,  -- I wonder what's inside... Could it be a scrum-diddly-umptious cake? But I've already gotten so roly-poly during the holiday season! Maybe I should just send it back!
        NO_THATARU_WOULDN_T_BE_RIGHT_BESIDES_IT                                   = 14147,  -- No, thataru wouldn't be right. Besides, it might not be edible. Anyway, please be sure to thank % for pudding the icing on such a delectable Starcake Chocolation. Ugh, I'm just terrible!
        WHY_WOULD_BE_SENDING_ME_A_GIFT_IT                                         = 14148,  -- Why would % be sending me a gift? It's not like there's anything special going on.
        THE_STARLIGHT_CELEBRATION_YOU_SAY_SO_THAT_EXPLAINS                        = 14149,  -- The Starlight Celebration, you say? So that explains the light shows and festive atmosphere around here lately. My head just hasn't been the same since I fell off that chocobo last month.
        I_BEST_START_LOOKING_FOR_SOMETHING_TO_GIVE                                = 14150,  -- I best start looking for something to give in return. In the meantime, please tell % how happy I am to have received this. And maybe next year I'll remember before it's too late. <Sigh>...One can only hope.
        A_PRESENT_FOR_ME_I_M_A_LONE                                               = 14151,  -- A present for me? I'm a lone lioness, and I don't need to share my kills with anyone!
        WHAT_WANTED_ME_TO_HAVE_THIS_WELL_I                                        = 14152,  -- What? % wanted me to have this? Well, I guess I could take it...
        DON_T_GET_THE_WRRRONG_IDEA_IT_S                                           = 14153,  -- Don't get the wrrrong idea! It's not like I enjoy the gift or anything! Just run back to % and drop dead! This conversation never happened!
        YOU_HAVE_RECEIVED                                                         = 14154,  -- You have received %!
        YOUR_HAS_BEEN_TAKEN                                                       = 14155,  -- Your % has been taken!
        YOU_HANDED_OVER                                                           = 14156,  -- You handed over %.
        VOIDWATCH_DEBUG_MENU_DO_NOTHING_OBTAIN_5_000                              = 14157,  -- Voidwatch debug menu. Do nothing. Obtain 5,000,000 cruor. Obtain necessary items. Obtain level one items.
        YOU_OBTAIN_A_FULL_SET_OF_VOIDWATCH_KEY                                    = 14158,  -- You obtain a full set of Voidwatch key items, and may now participate in any and all Voidwatch operations.
        YOU_NOW_HAVE_5_000_000_CRUOR                                              = 14159,  -- You now have 5,000,000 cruor!
        HAH_YAH_CAN_T_YE_SEE_I_M                                                  = 14160,  -- Hah! Yah! Can't ye see I'm... Wait a minute. I almost didn't recognize ye...
        LOOKS_LIKE_SOMEONE_S_COME_A_LONG_WAY                                      = 14161,  -- Looks like someone's come a long way since our last meetin'. Why don't I give ye somethin' that might help in yer training?
        BUT_FIRST_I_M_GONNA_NEED_PROOF_THAT                                       = 14162,  -- But first, I'm gonna need proof that ye're ready. %, %, and % should do the trick.
        DON_T_YE_GIVE_ME_THAT_FACE_IT                                             = 14163,  -- Don't ye give me that face. It's trainin'--it ain't supposed to be easy!
        BRING_ME_AND_AND_I_LL_GIVE_YE                                             = 14164,  -- Bring me %, %, and % and I'll give ye somethin' that should serve ye well.
        WELL_LOOKS_LIKE_SOMEONE_S_READY_FOR_HIS                                   = 14165,  -- Well, looks like someone's ready for his/her] next challenge. As promised, here's somethin' for ya.
        IT_S_A_PRESENT_FROM_OUR_FRIEND_CHAMAMA                                    = 14166,  -- It's a present from our friend Chamama. As for how it's going to help yer trainin', ye've got me...
        DAMN_IT_ALL_TO_HELL_I_KNOW_I                                              = 14167,  -- Damn it all to hell! I know I'd be able to make a bucketload of gil if I could help pioneer Adoulin...
        WAIT_WHO_ARE_YA_WHADDYA_DOIN_BOTHERIN_ME                                  = 14168,  -- Wait...who are ya? Whaddya doin' botherin' me?
        YA_DON_T_EVEN_KNOW_WHAT_PIONEERIN_IS                                      = 14169,  -- Ya don't even know what pioneerin' is?
        HMPH_SOME_ADVENTURER_YOU_ARE_EVEN_MY_GRANDMA                              = 14170,  -- Hmph. Some adventurer you are! Even my grandma keeps up with the times better'n that!
        SORRY_THAT_WAS_A_BIT_HARSH_OF_ME                                          = 14171,  -- ...Sorry. That was a bit harsh of me. Let me explain it to ya.
        YOU_VE_HEARD_OF_ADOULIN_RIGHT_TH_MARINE                                   = 14172,  -- You've heard of Adoulin, right? Th' marine trading city located way to th' west, across the Sea of Zafmlug?
        WELL_IT_TURNS_OUT_THERE_S_UNDEVELOPED_LAND                                = 14173,  -- Well, it turns out there's undeveloped land all around there. We're talking malms and malms of jungle. Lately there's been a huge push to reclaim that land and make it worth livin' on.
        DOESN_T_THAT_JUS_BEAT_ALL_PRISTINE_LAND                                   = 14174,  -- Doesn't that jus' beat all? Pristine land still exists, despite all th' progress we've made. Whaddaya think it's like out there?
        COURSE_NOT_E_RYONE_IS_FIT_TA_MAKE                                         = 14175,  -- 'Course, not e'ryone is fit ta make headway inta th' deep unknown, so they're lookin' for the meanest and leanest adventurers ta open up the land--and fast.
