        ID_14442                                                                  = 14442,  -- [Quests reset to initial settings/Key items reset to initial settings/All flags reset].
        DON_TCHA_THINK_DAT_FURROWED_BROW_AND_COCKED                               = 14443,  -- Don'tcha think dat furrowed brow and cocked head o' yers escaped me. Yer int'rested in dis chest, ain'tcha? Well, ya gots good right tah be, 'cause even us Gobbies is fascimanated wit' it. It's some sorta myst'ry box salvaged from a shipwreck in da Gugru Blue! Da mysterious part is dat what goes in don't necessarilies come out!
        WHILE_I_MAY_TOUT_ITS_AMAZIN_NESS_DON                                      = 14444,  -- While I may tout its amazin'ness, don'tcha think fer even a second dat I's at liberty tah divulge hows we came by it. Still, I likes yer face. It's a kind face, one dat says ya won't stabs me in da back, which is more'n I can say fer my own mum. Lemme shows ya how to use dis myst'ry box.
        BAH_DAH_BAH_DAHM_DAH_DAAAHM_YA_OPEN                                       = 14445,  -- Bah-dah-bah-dahm dah-daaahm! Ya open da chest. Dat's it. And da kicker be dat I'm da one doin' da openin'. Ya just gets tah stand dere gawkin' in astonishmament. Easy gig, no?
        OH_YEAH_FORE_I_FORGET_WHAT_GOOD_S                                         = 14446,  -- Oh yeah, 'fore I forget. What good's a chest if ya ain't gots da key? Well, da key to dis chest is da fine art o' waitin'.
        YA_WANTSA_KNOW_DA_HOWS_N_DA_WHYS                                          = 14447,  -- Ya wantsa know da hows n' da whys? Well da bosses had our tinkers tinkerin' on troo' da night and dey foun' dat...
        WELL_DEY_FOUN_DAT_WE_REALLY_GOTS_NO                                       = 14448,  -- Well, dey foun' dat we really gots no idea why da loot changes. Anywho, ya's wanna wait 'n wait 'n wait, den keep on waitin' some more. "Good things come tah dose who wait," right? Well, da longer ya wait, da gooder da thing...maybe. Ya just never know wit' a myst'ry box.
        ALSO_I_CALLS_DA_AMOUNT_O_TIME_YA                                          = 14449,  -- Also, I calls da amount o' time ya's waited yer circa...circama...circamadamian...ugh, yer daily tally. It ain't just da name dat's catchy, though. Da higher yer tally, da gooder yer goods get! Can't get much good--er, simpler dan dat.
        FINALLY_YA_OPENS_DA_CHEST_OOOH_I_CAN                                      = 14450,  -- Finally, ya opens da chest. Oooh, I can barely contain m'self thinkin' o' all da riches I--er, ya could have!
        OH_DAT_S_RIGHT_HEYHEYHEY_GOT_ANY_ITEMS                                    = 14451,  -- Oh, dat's right! Heyheyhey, got any items ya won't be needin'? If so, fork 'em over 'n yer daily tally'll increase! Mebbe not by much, but dat's better'n nothin', am I right?
        AND_DERE_S_NO_BETTER_FEELIN_DAN_TAKIN                                     = 14452,  -- And dere's no better feelin' dan takin' trash and turnin' it into treasure. It's pramactically a new kind o' alchemy! But don't go gung ho 'n overfills da thing 'til its hinges break. Myst'ry boxes don't grow on goobbues, y'know.
        PLUS_I_LL_BE_HERE_TAH_STOPS_YA                                            = 14453,  -- Plus, I'll be here tah stops ya if I sees ya stuffin' whole Gobbiebags worth o' possessions in dere, so don't worry yer oversized noggin' over and over over it. Whats was I sayin' again? Ugh, never mind.
        SADLY_HOWSEVER_ANODDA_MYST_RY_BOUT_DIS_CHEST                              = 14454,  -- Sadly, howsever, anodda myst'ry 'bout dis chest is dat it won't takes just any ol' bauble. It has da taste o' a picky peiste--it feasts upon nothin' but da rarest and unique-est o' artifacts.
        LASTLY_SINCE_WE_DON_T_KNOWS_WHERE_DA                                      = 14455,  -- Lastly, since we don't knows where da items go once inside, ya ain't gettin' nothin' back datcha put in. Ya reap whatcha sow, and da weather ain't always condusimasive to a good harvest, am I right? My condolemances in advance for any losses ya mights incur from da myst'ry box's fickle nature.
        DAT_ALL_MAKE_NOUGH_SENSE_TAH_YA_JUST                                      = 14456,  -- Dat all make 'nough sense tah ya? Just say da woid when ya wanna use my services. I's more'n happy tah help.
        HEY_I_REM_MBER_SEEIN_YER_FOICE_ROUND                                      = 14457,  -- Hey! I rem'mber seein' yer foice 'round here. Take a looksie. I's taken' it upon myself tah jigger 'round wit' dese all-new myst'ry boxes, found straight from an ol' capsized vessel in the Gugru Blue.
        I_S_NEVAH_GONNA_SAY_HOW_WE_GOTS                                           = 14458,  -- I's nevah gonna say how we gots our hands on 'em, so dun even ask! But, still, I gots tah say dat dese're somet'in' special! Now try yer hand 'fore I smack ya!
        JUST_SELECT_YER_DESIR_D_DIAL_AND_PLUG                                     = 14459,  -- Just select yer desir'd dial and plug 'way at it. Will ya win somethin' super special? Or will't be da booby proize?
        DESE_RE_SOME_SPECIAL_DIALS_AN_I_GOTS                                      = 14460,  -- Dese're some special dials, an' I gots no inklin' what's inside. Ya gots tah open 'em yerself tah find out what treasures lie within!
        OH_HO_I_S_FORGETTIN_TAH_EXPLAIN_SOMETHIN                                  = 14461,  -- Oh ho, I's forgettin' tah explain somethin' to ya. See dese special dials? Dey're super primo, but I still no know wut's gonna be in dere.
        SO_I_S_NOT_BE_TAKIN_NO_RESPONSIBILITY                                     = 14462,  -- So I's not be takin' no responsibility if somethin' weird 'n wacky comes out. Got it? Ya open it, ya keep it.
        N_OPENIN_EM_REQUIRES_SOME_KINDA_SECRET_TECHNIQUE                          = 14463,  -- 'N openin' 'em requires some kinda secret technique. Maybe it'll succeed, maybe tha box'll break. 'Sif I know. But ya can only try 'em once a day.
        OHO_YA_FEELIN_LUCKY_NOUGH_TAH_TAKES_A                                     = 14464,  -- Oho, ya feelin' lucky 'nough tah takes a stab at da myst'ry box?
        WHATCHA_GONNA_DO_TALLY_OPEN_THE_BOX_AND                                   = 14465,  -- Whatcha gonna do? (# tally) Open the box and profit! Listen to the explanation. Inquire about my daily tally. Peek at some possibilities. Nothing right now.
        YA_WANNA_OPEN_DAT_SUCKER_UP_OKAY_BUT                                      = 14466,  -- Ya wanna open dat sucker up? Okay, but which dial ya be wantin'?
        DAT_S_DA_SPIRIT_SO_WHICH_DIAL_YA                                          = 14467,  -- Dat's da spirit! So which dial ya be wantin'?
        SO_WHAT_DIAL_YA_GONNA_PICK_TALLY_I                                        = 14468,  -- So, what dial ya gonna pick? (# tally) I got cold feet, so none. Dial 1 (Materials): # tally. Dial 2 (Food): # tally. Dial 3 (Medicine): # tally. Dial 4 (Sundries 1): # tally. Dial 5 (Sundries 2): # tally. Special dial: # tally [/ (already opened)]. Adoulin dial: # tally[/ (already opened)]. Pictlogica dial: # tally[/ (already opened)]. @ @ @ Wanted dial: # tally[/ (already opened)]. @ @
        YER_GOIN_WIT_DIAL_HUH_WHATCHU_TRYIN_TA                                    = 14469,  -- Yer goin' wit' dial #, huh? Whatchu tryin' ta pull!? Yer daily tally's too low.
        YER_GOIN_WIT_DIAL_HUH_LESSEE_WHAT_MYST                                    = 14470,  -- Yer goin' wit' dial #, huh? Lessee what myst'ries await!
        DIS_BOX_IS_FULL_O_MYST_RIES_T                                             = 14471,  -- Dis box is full o' myst'ries,t Dat span da realm's his'try,t So whatcha gonna get from da chest...o'...uh, fortunery?t
        OOOH_LOOKS_AT_WHAT_POPPED_OUT_I_HOPES                                     = 14472,  -- Oooh, looks at what popped out! I hopes it makes yer adventures dat much more adventumarous!
        YA_S_THOUGHT_I_THREW_YER_PRIZE_AWAY                                       = 14473,  -- Ya's thought I threw yer prize away?! Prepostamarous! I's just tucked it away for safekeepin' is all.
        YOU_HAVE_USED_OF_YOUR_DAILY_TALLY                                         = 14474,  -- You have used # [point/points] of your daily tally!
        WANNA_GO_AGAIN                                                            = 14475,  -- Wanna go again?
        KEEP_GOIN_LEMME_AT_IT_THANKS_BUT_NO                                       = 14476,  -- Keep goin'? Lemme at it! Thanks, but no thanks.
        YER_DAILY_TALLY_IT_S_UM_Y_KNOW                                            = 14477,  -- Yer daily tally? It's, um... Y'know, 'round # [point/points] or thereamabouts.
        LEMME_CHECK_FOR_YA_WELL_IT_COULDA_BEEN                                    = 14478,  -- Lemme check for ya! Well, it coulda been %, %, or mebbe even %. What? Ya thinks ya could do better wit' one o' dese Gobbie masks on!?
        ANYWISE_WHERE_D_DA_MYST_RY_BE_IF                                          = 14479,  -- Anywise, where'd da myst'ry be if ya's knew da answer 'fore ya opens it?
        SOME_THINGS_IS_BETTER_LEFT_UNKNOWN_GOTTA_LEAVE                            = 14480,  -- Some things is better left unknown. Gotta leave a little room fer romanchismo in da woild, y'know.
        DERE_WE_GOES_DA_MYST_RY_BOX_SEEMS                                         = 14481,  -- Dere we goes. Da myst'ry box seems tah like yer offerin'...but it wants more. Got anythin' else ya wanna throw away?
        DERE_WE_GOES_OHO_LOOKS_LIKE_IT_DON                                        = 14482,  -- Dere we goes. Oho, looks like it don't wants no more. Guess ya gotta come back tomorrow if ya's wanna keep gettin' rid o' stuff.
        YER_DAILY_TALLY_S_INCREASED                                               = 14483,  -- Yer daily tally's increased [a smidge./someamawhats./a Gobby-fold!/a ginormagantic amount!]
        SORRAH_BUT_IT_WON_T_LEMME_PUT_DIS                                         = 14484,  -- Sorrah, but it won't lemme put dis in. Got anythin' it mights like better?
        SORRAH_BUT_DA_CHEST_HAS_DAT_LOOK_Y                                        = 14485,  -- Sorrah, but da chest has dat look. Y'know, da one dat says, "I'll kills ya if ya tries tah give me dat." I guess alls ya can do is comes back some odda time.
        NAH_IT_JUST_WON_T_WOIK_I_S                                                = 14486,  -- Nah, it just won't woik. I's did my best, but yer daily tally just won't go no higher. Ya ain't gonna get no prizes by hoardin' yer points, so stop bein' such a Greedalox and use 'em.
        GIL_LOVIN_GOBBIES_YA_S_HIT_DA_JACKPOT                                     = 14487,  -- Gil-lovin' Gobbies, %, ya's hit da jackpot! I's so happy for ya I think I's gettin' da vapors.
        OBTAINS                                                                   = 14488,  -- % obtains %!
        WHOAWHOAWHOA_IF_YA_S_GOT_BUSINESS_WIT_DA                                  = 14489,  -- Whoawhoawhoa! If ya's got business wit' da box, ya foist gots business wit' me. Whatcha need?
        SO_YA_BE_WANTIN_THE_SPECIAL_DIAL_WHOAWHOAWHOA                             = 14490,  -- So ya be wantin' the special dial? Whoawhoawhoa! Get yer grubby hands offa that! Ya don't have enough daily tally, and I's not 'bout tah let ya cheat me!
        SO_YA_BE_WANTIN_THE_DIAL_M_KAY                                            = 14491,  -- So ya be wantin' the [special/Adoulin/pictlogica/Wanted/campaign] dial? M'kay, get yerself all steeled up, 'cause here we go! 'Member, no complaints!
        SO_YA_BE_WANTIN_THE_DIAL_WHOAWHOAWHOA_GET                                 = 14492,  -- So ya be wantin' the [special/Adoulin/pictlogica/Wanted] dial? Whoawhoawhoa! Get yer grubby hands offa that! I's already opened one fer ya today! Haul that keister outta here and come back t'morrow.
        OY_WOULD_YA_GET_A_LOOK_AT_YER                                             = 14493,  -- Oy, would ya get a look at yer %! I guess I can let ya open [/Dial 1/Dial 2/Dial 3/Dial 4/Dial 5/the special dial///the abjuration dial/the fortune dial/the furnishings dial//the Vana'versary dial/the festival dial] whenever ya want fer not a single onz o' daily tally!
        DUN_THINK_THAT_I_S_BE_A_GIL                                               = 14494,  -- Dun think that I's be a gil-grubbin' good-fer-nuthin'. If'n ya dun wanna open any dial, then I gives ya back yer %.
        YER_EYES_BE_BIGGER_N_YER_STOMACH_IF                                       = 14495,  -- Yer eyes be bigger'n yer stomach. If'n ya wanna open [/Dial 1/Dial 2/Dial 3/Dial 4/Dial 5/the Special Dial///the abjuration dial/the fortune dial/the furnishings dial//the Vana'versary dial/the festival diaal] usin' yer %, then ya gotta make room in yer bags!
        WHAT_S_BE_DIS_WHAT_M_I_PPOSED                                             = 14496,  -- What's be dis? %? What'm I 'pposed ta do wit it? I dun have any clue how ta use it, so take it home wit ya.
        ID_14497                                                                  = 14497,  -- #<#
        URK                                                                       = 14498,  -- Urk!
        I_UNDERSTAND_THAT_YOU_ARE_AN_ADVENTURER_MY                                = 14499,  -- I understand that you are...an adventurer? My name is Pieuje I. d'Oraguille, commander of San d'Oria's famed Temple Knights.
        IS_THAT_S_VOICE_I_HEAR                                                    = 14500,  -- Is that %'s voice I hear?
        FORGIVE_ME_BUT_I_AM_MORE_ACCUSTOMED_TO                                    = 14501,  -- Forgive me, but I am more accustomed to recognizing faces than voices, especially through such a peculiar device.
        I_MUST_THANK_YOU_FOR_YOUR_HANDLING_OF                                     = 14502,  -- I must thank you for your handling of the Altedour incident in Fei'Yin.
        NEVER_ONCE_HAVE_I_FORGOTTEN_YOUR_DEDICATION_TO                            = 14503,  -- Never once have I forgotten your dedication to protecting all of San d'Oria.
        AS_YOU_ARE_DOUBTLESSLY_AWARE_A_SHORT_TIME                                 = 14504,  -- As you are doubtlessly aware, a short time ago I received a memorandum from the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network detailing Unity Concord and requesting my services as a Unity leader.
        TELL_ME_IS_THERE_ANY_GREATER_WAY_FOR                                      = 14505,  -- Tell me. Is there any greater way for a prince regent to earn honor for his kingdom than by spearheading a group dedicated to purging evil from the land?
        MANY_AROUND_ME_WERE_OPPOSED_BUT_THAT_BOTHERED                             = 14506,  -- Many around me were opposed, but that bothered me not. My brother, Trion, serves as a representative of the Trust initiative, and it falls to me to up the ante.
        I_CANNOT_LIE_THAT_WAS_AN_IMPORTANT_FACTOR                                 = 14507,  -- I cannot lie. That was an important factor in my decision.
        BUT_BE_NOT_CONCERNED_WITH_OUR_INTERNAL_SQUABBLES                          = 14508,  -- But be not concerned with our internal squabbles. Know only that it pleases me to welcome you to my Unity.
        MY_NAME_IS_AYAME_A_RANKING_MEMBER_OF                                      = 14509,  -- My name is Ayame, a ranking member of the Mythril Musketeers. Pleased to make your acquaintance.
        HAHA_YES_OF_COURSE_I_REMEMBER_YOU_HOW                                     = 14510,  -- Haha...yes, %, of course I remember you. How characteristic of you to have your fingers in everyone's pies.
        DO_NOT_THINK_ME_UNGRATEFUL_NO_I_AM                                        = 14511,  -- Do not think me ungrateful. No, I am always pleased to have your help, but this time things are a bit different.
        DO_NOT_THINK_ME_UNGRATEFUL_YOU_STRENGTHENED_THE                           = 14512,  -- Do not think me ungrateful. You strengthened the Mythril Musketeers in ways I never thought possible, and we are closer than ever before.
        NOT_TERRIBLY_LONG_AGO_I_WAS_CONTACTED_BY                                  = 14513,  -- Not terribly long ago I was contacted by the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network, which asked that I head a Unity.
        AT_FIRST_I_WAS_FLUSTERED_AND_THOUGHT_OF                                   = 14514,  -- At first I was flustered and thought of turning the offer down. Why would they pick me when there are others more qualified?
        BUT_VOLKER_DECIDED_IT_WOULD_BE_THE_PERFECT                                = 14515,  -- But Volker decided it would be the perfect opportunity for me to develop my leadership skills, and told them I would accept...without my knowledge.
        THOUGH_UNCONVINCED_THAT_I_AM_THE_BEST_FIT                                 = 14516,  -- Though unconvinced that I am the best fit, I pledge to dedicate myself wholly to this endeavor.
        PEOPLE_ARE_COUNTING_ON_ME_NOT_ONLY_VOLKER                                 = 14517,  -- People are counting on me. Not only Volker, but those like you who have pledged their support.
        I_WILL_NOT_LET_YOU_DOWN                                                   = 14518,  -- I will not let you down.
        STAND_SHARP_MAGGOT_I_VE_GOT_NO_TIME                                       = 14519,  -- Stand sharp, maggot! I've got no time for people who're gonna slack off!
        WAIT_THAT_S_YOU_ISN_T_IT                                                  = 14520,  -- ...Wait. That's you, isn't it, %?
        I_HEAR_YOU_VE_DECIDED_TO_JOIN_MY                                          = 14521,  -- I hear you've decided to join my backbreaking Unity.
        WELL_WHAT_VE_YOU_GOT_TO_SAY_FOR                                           = 14522,  -- Well!? What've you got to say for yourself!?
        HOW_DO_YOU_RESPOND_THAT_S_RIGHT_NOPE                                      = 14523,  -- How do you respond? That's right. Nope. Y-yessir!
        IMPUDENT_CRETIN_YOU_SAY_SIR_WHEN_ADDRESSING_A                             = 14524,  -- Impudent cretin! You say sir when addressing a superior officer!
        BETTER_EVERYONE_IN_MY_UNITY_IS_EQUAL_YOU                                  = 14525,  -- Better. Everyone in my Unity is equal--you're all worthless whelps!
        WE_DON_T_CODDLE_THE_WEAK_AROUND_HERE                                      = 14526,  -- We don't coddle the weak around here. If you want respect, you earn it.
        UNTIL_THEN_YOU_RE_JUST_A_DRIED_UP                                         = 14527,  -- Until then, you're just a dried-up, shriveled worm!
        SO_GO_CRAWLING_AROUND_IN_THE_DIRT_AND                                     = 14528,  -- So go crawling around in the dirt and pray some crow doesn't sweep down and gobble you up!
        NOW_GET_OUT_THERE                                                         = 14529,  -- Now get out there!
        HELLO_GOOD_ADVENTURER_YOU_CAN_CALL_ME_APURURU                             = 14530,  -- Hello, good adventurer. You can call me Apururu.
        IS_THAT_AM_I_RIGHTARU                                                     = 14531,  -- Is that...%? Am I rightaru?
        YOUR_GOOD_DEEDS_ON_BEHALF_OF_WINDURSTARU_HAVE                             = 14532,  -- Your good deeds on behalf of Windurstaru have not gone unnoticed.
        I_M_SO_WORRIED_ABOUT_MY_BROTHER_BUT                                       = 14533,  -- I'm so worried about my brother...but if this is one way for me to help-welp him, then so be it.
