        OH_LOOK_ANOTHER_ADVENTURER_IN_DESPERATE_NEED_OF                           = 15267,  -- Oh, look! Another adventurer in desperate need of my most accurate fashion advice. Tell me--what can the stylist extraordinaire Brygid recommend for you?
