        I_VE_CONVINCED_ALL_THE_MOVERS_AND_SHAKERS                                 = 15271,  -- I've convinced all the movers and shakers in Bastok to assist me in holding the most amazing fashion show the city--no, all of Vana'diel!--has ever seen!
        I_VE_CONVINCED_ALL_THE_MOVERS_AND_SHAKERS_2                               = 15272,  -- I've convinced all the movers and shakers in Bastok to assist me in holding the most amazing fashion show the city--no, all of Vana'diel!--has ever seen!
