        YOU_SEE_I_VE_CONVINCED_ALL_THE_MOVERS                                     = 15275,  -- You see, I've convinced all the movers and shakers in Bastok to assist me in holding the most amazing fashion show the city--no, all of Vana'diel!--has ever seen!
        THE_CITY_IS_HOPING_THAT_THIS_INITIATIVE_WILL                              = 15276,  -- The city is hoping that this initiative will help stimulate the local economy, bringing in people from far and wide to spend, spend, spend!
